<p>尊敬的 {!Internal_Registration__c.Name_CN__c}，</p>
<br/>
<p>第137届广交会的会议室预定将于北京时间2025年4月7日16:00开放。如有预定需求，请您及时登录【信鸿—应用中心—国际营销展会系统—会议预定】进行操作。</p>
<br/>
<p>本届广交会展厅配备两间会议室，其中VIP1可容纳8-10人，VIP2可容纳4-6人。因今年二楼会谈区面积大幅缩减，会议室资源紧张，单个客户可预约的会议室时长为1小时。请勿多次预定以延长会议时间，如发现此类行为，系统后台将自动取消相关会议室的占用。如需查询目前会议室整体已预定情况，可登录展会系统—会议预定—预定详情进行查看。预定后如需取消，请及时登录展会系统进行操作，请勿造成会议室资源空置、浪费，谢谢！</p>
<br/>
<img src="data:image/png;base64," alt=""/>
<br/>
<br/>
<p>Dear {!Internal_Registration__c.Name_EN__c}，</p>
<br/>
<p>The conference room booking of 137th Canton Fair is scheduled to open at 16:00 Beijing time on April 7, 2025. If you have any reservation needs, please log in to [Xinhong - Application Center - Exhibition System - Conference Room Reservation] in time to operate.</p>
<br/>
<p>The exhibition hall of 137th Canton Fair is equipped with two conference rooms, of which VIP1 can accommodate 8-10 people and VIP2 can accommodate 4-6 people. Due to the significant reduction in the meeting area on the 2nd floor this time, the meeting room that a single customer can reserve is 1 hour. Please do not book multiple times to extend the meeting time, if such behavior is found, the system will automatically cancel the reservation of the relevant meeting room. If you need to check the overall booking status of both conference rooms, you can log in to the Exhibition system - Conference Reservation - reservation details to view.</p>
<br/>
<p>If you need to cancel after booking, please log in to the exhibition system in time to operate. Please do not cause empty and waste of conference room resources, thank you!</p>
<br/>